# Force LF for all text files, on every machine regardless of core.autocrlf.
# Motivation (PR #1 follow-up): scripts/make_plugin.py copies working-tree
# bytes into dist/ verbatim (shutil.copy2), so a contributor checkout with
# autocrlf=true would materialize CRLF files and leak them into the shipped
# plugin — the same defect class PR #1 fixed for builder-written files.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Build artifact is a zip (gitignored, but guard against future tracking).
*.plugin binary
